snippet.title: Action Arcade Wrestling 2 (7/29/2013)
snippet.description:
Official description: The sequel to the best-selling XBLI game, AAW2 is a 2.5D retro arcade game. Hundreds of moves, multiple match types, create wrestlers & arenas, up to 10 wrestlers in the ring at once, classic control scheme and so much more.

RELEASE DATE: 7/29/2013
DEVELOPER: Action937
GENRE: Sports & Recreation
Offline players 1 - 4
Offline co-op 2 - 4
